quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  62,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino seninnde Allah, Laam…óo, Senii…óo, Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo On"
  62,2,"Ko kanko nuli e humammbinnee…ďe …ďen Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, himo janngana …ďe Aayeeje Makko …óen, o la…ď…ďina …ďe, o anndina …ďe Deftere nden e Sunna on, hay si tawiino ko adii …óum, …ďe laatino e majjere …ďanngude"
  62,3,"(O nuli mo) kadi e wo…ó…ďe goo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe hawrondiraali e …ďen taho. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo On"
  62,4,"∆äum ko …ďural Allah, Himo okka ngal mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom …ďural mawnngal"
  62,5,"Misal ronndinaa…ďe Tawreeta …ďen refti …ďe golliraali nde, no wa'i wa mbabba ronndii mba defte. Misal yim…ďe fennoo…ďe Aayeeje Alla …óen bonii. Allah fewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  62,6,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo HuudiŇčkoo…ďe ! Si on aa∆īike wonnde ko on yi…óaa…ďe Allah ko wanaa yim…ďe heddii…ďe …ďen, haray yelee maayde, si tawii ko on goongu…ďe"
  62,7,"∆Āe yelotaako nde muk, sabu ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardini kon. Allah ko anndu…óo too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  62,8,"Maaku: \"Ndee maayde nde dogoton, pellet, ko nde hawraynde e mon. Refti rutte…óon ka On anndu…óo wirnii…ói e fee√Īu…ói, O humpita on ko gollayno…óon kon"
  62,9,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe ! Si juulde nden noddinanaama √Īalnde Juma, yaccee e jantagol Allah, acciton ngeyngu. Ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on, si tawno ko on anndu…ďe"
  62,10,"Si julde nden gasii, haray saakitee ka leydi, …óa…ď…ďon …ďural Allah ngal [woni arsike], janntoron innde Allah ko …óuu…ói, belajo'o on maloyte"
  62,11,"Si …ďe yi'ii ngeyngu maa fijindaaru, …ďe hammira ton, …ďe acce hi…óa darii. Maaku: \"Ko ko woni ka Allah kon …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude belee…óe e njulaaku. Ko Allah …ďuri Mo∆ī∆īude e arsikoo…ďe …ďen"
  63,1,"Si naafiqii…ďe …ďen arii e maa, …ďe wi'a: \"Me…óen seedii wonnde ko a Nulaa…óo Allah\". Allah no anndi wonnde pellet, ko a Nulaa…óo Makko; Allah no seedii wonnde pellet, naafiqii…ďe …ďen ko fenoo…ďe"
  63,2,"∆Āe jogitorri goondooje ma…ď…ďe …óen heedo, …ďe sakkii laawol Allah ngol. Pellet, fii ko …ďe gollaynoo kon bonii"
  63,3,"∆äum non ko tawde …ďe gom…óinii, refti …ďe yeddi, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen notaa e mun; kam…ďe on …ďe faamataa"